_:Nb3c3f79c5dcc4da0b914bd947ac786d4 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Vicky Bennett is General Counsel at Sellafield Ltd.</p>\n\n<p>She has a strong track record of advising organisations operating in complex, highly regulated environments, particularly within the nuclear sector.</p>\n\n<p>As General Counsel for Sellafield Ltd, Vicky provides legal leadership across a wide range of activities, supporting sound decision-making and effective governance focussed on enabling progress on long-term, nationally significant programmes.</p>\n\n<p>In her previous role. Vicky was part of the executive team at <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/nuclear-waste-services\">Nuclear Waste Services Ltd</a>.</p>\n\n<p>During this time Vicky brought her experience to enable corporate transformation programmes and oversee the provision of advice on complex regulatory matters and the delivery of major infrastructure projects.</p>\n\n<p>Vicky’s work is guided by integrity, pragmatism and supporting the mission. She provides clear, proportionate legal advice that balances risk, accountability, and delivery. She is also committed to developing high-performing legal teams, creating an environment in which people are empowered to contribute meaningfully and make a positive impact on the organisations they support.</p>\n" .
_:N068524e98dc3414b90b59269a8870f20 <http://schema.org/item> <https://www.gov.uk/> .
